title: NIVEA Skin Firming & Smoothing Concentrated Serum, 2.5 Ounce
Neem Clay Face Mask
description:
Our Neem Clay Face Mask is in high demand! This natural face pack is an all-natural blend of deeply cleansing French clay, healing Neem leaves, and hydrating oils. It draws out impurities and promotes clear and healthy skin. No Sulfates, Parabens, or Phthalates are used.  Gluten free. All of JustNeem's products are made with natural Neem from Mauritania. Neem has been revered for thousands of years by ancient Eastern cultures for its healing properties. Neem is refered to as "nature's pharmacy" and is a traditional treatment for acne, psoriasis, eczema, athlete's foot, and many other skin disorders. 10% of proceeds go to improve the lives of the people and the economy of Mauritania, West Africa.

title: Lolita Lempicka By Lolita Lempicka For Women. Eau De Parfum Spray 3.4 Oz.
description: Introduced in 1997. Fragrance notes: exotic licorice and vanilla combined with light greens, florals and musk. Recommended use: daytime.When applying any fragrance please consider that there are several factors which can affect the natural smell of your skin and, in turn, the way a scent smells on you.  For instance, your mood, stress level, age, body chemistry, diet, and current medications may all alter the scents you wear.  Similarly, factor such as dry or oily skin can even affect the amount of time a fragrance will last after being applied
